member.name: FXEQ_PARAMETERS
member.summary: Parameters for use with the FXEQ XAPO.

member.name: FXEQ_PARAMETERS.FrequencyCenter0
member.summary: Center frequency in Hz for band 0. Must be between FXEQ_MIN_FREQUENCY_CENTER and FXEQ_MAX_FREQUENCY_CENTER.

member.name: FXEQ_PARAMETERS.Gain0
member.summary: The boost or decrease to frequencies in band 0. Must be between FXEQ_MIN_GAIN and FXEQ_MAX_GAIN

member.name: FXEQ_PARAMETERS.Bandwidth0
member.summary: Width of band 0. Must be between FXEQ_MIN_BANDWIDTH and FXEQ_MAX_BANDWIDTH.
